headline: This Incredibly Cheap Tech Stock Is Soaring, and Artificial Intelligence (AI) Could Send It Higher in 2025 and Beyond
summary: Shares of contract electronics manufacturer Jabil (NYSE: JBL) have been in fine form over the last few months thanks to its solid quarterly results, and the good news is that the company looks set to enter the new year with momentum on its side following its latest report.  Jabil released its fiscal 2025 first-quarter results (for the three months ended Nov. 30) on Dec. 18.  The stock jumped as the company's numbers were well ahead of Wall Street's expectations.
